name: ValidateTest
description: Unit tests for the Validate class, focusing on validation methods like notNull and notNullParam.

test_cases.name: testNotNull
test_cases.description: Tests the notNull method of the Validate class to ensure it correctly handles non-null and null inputs.

test_cases.description: Tests the notNullParam method of the Validate class to ensure it correctly handles null inputs and provides the correct error message.
